1) Replace all of the following placeholders with actual values

		$PROJECT_GROUP_ID$
		$PROJECT_ARTIFACT_ID$
		$PROJECT_NAME$
		$REPO_OWNER$
		$REPO_NAME$
		$BINTRAY_USERNAME$

   in the following files:

		pom.xml
		.github/workflows-template/perform-release.yaml

2) Add a new package with the name `$REPO_NAME$` under Bintray -> $REPO_OWNER$ -> repositories -> maven-repo.

3) Add the following secrets under GitHub -> Project -> Settings -> Secrets:

		GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN
		BINTRAY_API_KEY

   The `GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN` must have the full repo scope and the full packages scope.
   The `BINTRAY_API_KEY` must belong to the above mentioned `$BINTRAY_USERNAME$`.

4) Rename the directory `.github/workflows-template` to `.github/workflows`.

5) Afterwards this `FIRST STEPS` file can be deleted.

6) Commit and push the changes. You are ready to go ...
